h2#location Location

:markdown
  Join Zeke, Jenelle, and Cosmos this summer for a celebration of love with our closest friends and relatives. The ceremony and 
  reception will be held at the [Montclair Women's Cultural Arts 
  Club](http://goo.gl/raRba3) in the hills of Oakland, California. This charming venue is 30 minutes from San Francisco by car, and 
  about an hour from Napa or Sonoma.  

h2#schedule Schedule

