  The basic schedule is this: On **Saturday**, the ceremony and reception will 
  be held at the [Montclair Women's Cultural Arts Club](http://goo.gl/raRba3) 
  in Oakland. On **Sunday**, we'll host a picnic in San Francisco's [Golden 
  Gate Park](http://www.golden-gate-park.com/). Expect an email and a website 
