h2#travel Travel
  
:markdown
  If you're flying, you'll want land at **OAK** or **SFO**. To search 
  for cheap flights, try [google.com/flights](http://goo.gl/vdX9Hn), 
  which has fares for most popular airlines. Give 
  [southwest.com](https://www.southwest.com/) a try too, as their flights are 
  not listed by any other service. 
  

  If you're coming by train, take the [California 
  Zephyr](http://www.amtrak.com/california-zephyr-train) or the [Coast 
  Starlight](http://www.amtrak.com/coast-starlight-train) to Emeryville or 
  Jack London Square in Oakland. 
  
  We recommend renting a car if you are flying or taking a train. 

  If you're driving, you're driving.  

